a relatively slow weapon and we got into it and I think he agreed with me, but I have met many who use the powerful/slow weapon in off-hand. I know with such weapon upgrades as there are in Vex thal etc that weapons dmg/dly ratio is getting even more better, for instance say you have a lvl 20 monk with a  SoS (17/28?) and a Wu's stick (7/18?) which hand would you place each in? I would put SoS in main and Wu's in off-hand.  Just a thing I often ponder <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>-Till<br>p.s Excuse my poor grammar,spelling ...you name it! Its 1:30am and I generally suck at it anyway <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/utilluinmt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tilluin mt</A> at: 8/11/02 7:25:55 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/unolacola.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nolacola</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#628CBC>(8/11/02 7:48:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=198.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: duel wield</span><hr size=1> you put wu's in primary hand because its faster, because its faster you get more use out of the damage bonus on your main hand. <p>Aerwen - 53 Ranger<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65702">My Magelo Profile</a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/ufogelxanedu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fogel Xanedu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>QHills and Clueless</span><br> 