r><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~anax/DhamSig.gif"></center><br><center>Half Elf Warlord - Ded Seksay</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/ujasminne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jasminne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#628CBC>(8/11/02 8:58:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=198.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eqronins.com/ronin_logo_new.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> I don't mean to come off sounding like an ass, but I believe the proper term is &quot;dual wielding&quot; not &quot;duel.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/ufaultless.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faultless</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#628CBC>(8/11/02 9:55:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=198.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> Hush Jassy.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/ujasminne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jasminne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#628CBC>(8/11/02 9:56:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm1.showAddReply